# Employee Attendance System â€“ Frontend

The Employee Attendance System is a web application that allows employees to mark their daily attendance and managers to monitor team attendance efficiently. It provides secure login, real-time attendance tracking, and dashboard views using a modern web interface.

This is the frontend application built using React, which provides user interfaces for Employees and Managers to interact with the attendance system.

